        <p style="font-size:0.9375rem;color:var(--color-muted);line-height:1.7">
            This Privacy Policy describes how MyBabyGuessr collects, uses and protects your personal data, in accordance with the <strong>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR — EU 2016/679)</strong>.
