        </p>

        <h2 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--color-ink);margin:2rem 0 0.625rem;padding-bottom:0.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-line)">2. Data We Collect</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.9375rem;color:var(--color-muted);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:0.75rem"><strong style="color:var(--color-ink)">For organizer accounts</strong> (registration required):</p>
        <ul style="margin:0 0 1rem 1.25rem;font-size:0.9375rem;color:var(--color-muted);line-height:1.9;list-style:disc">
