        <h2 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--color-ink);margin:2rem 0 0.625rem;padding-bottom:0.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-line)">4. Data Retention</h2>
        <ul style="margin:0 0 0 1.25rem;font-size:0.9375rem;color:var(--color-muted);line-height:1.9;list-style:disc">
            <li><strong style="color:var(--color-ink)">Account data</strong>: retained until account deletion, then purged within 30 days.</li>
            <li><strong style="color:var(--color-ink)">Games and guesses</strong>: linked to the account, deleted at the same time.</li>
