            <li><strong style="color:var(--color-ink)">Uploaded images</strong>: deleted when the game or account is deleted.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--color-ink);margin:2rem 0 0.625rem;padding-bottom:0.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-line)">5. Hosting and Recipients</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.9375rem;color:var(--color-muted);line-height:1.7">
            Your data is hosted exclusively by <strong style="color:var(--color-ink)">o2switch</strong> (222-224 Boulevard Gustave Flaubert, 63000 Clermont-Ferrand, France), a web hosting provider acting as a data processor.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:0.9375rem;color:var(--color-muted);line-height:1.7;margin-top:0.75rem">
