        <h2 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--color-ink);margin:2rem 0 0.625rem;padding-bottom:0.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-line)">6. International Transfers</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.9375rem;color:var(--color-muted);line-height:1.7">
            All data is hosted in France. <strong>No transfer to countries outside the European Union</strong> is performed.
